ki.jp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">//ensemble.kamitsubaki.jp/</a><br />・Steam商店页面： <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2581050/_/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://store.steampowered.com/app/2581050/_/</a><br />・官方X（旧Twitter）：https: <a href="https://twitter.com/ensembleJP_k" target="_blank" rel="noopener">//twitter.com/ensembleJP_k</a></p><h2> “关椿市音乐会正在进行中。 》标题详情</h2><p>-与你和你的心一起玩的节奏游戏-<br />类型：节奏游戏 玩家人数：1 支持语言：日语 / 英语 / 简体中文 / 繁体中文 / 韩语平台：Steam / iOS / Android<br />发售日期：2024年期间（计划）<br />价格：待定制作：KAMITSUBAKI STUDIO<br />制作：拉拉拉工作室<br />音乐制作/合作：HARD CORE TANO*C<br />实施：Rocket Studio</p><h3>故事</h3><p>背景是一个崩溃的世界。在那里，AI女孩们苏醒了，她们的目标是通过一首名为“魔法”的特殊歌曲的力量来“振兴世界”。</p><p>世界为何崩溃？他们存在的理由是什么？这一切都在演唱会的最后，请大家自行观看。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/04906b35de1c97930715a3bf1c4ea200-kix.v5ufyvu2kvi7-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/04906b35de1c97930715a3bf1c4ea200-kix.v5ufyvu2kvi7-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/04906b35de1c97930715a3bf1c4ea200-kix.v5ufyvu2kvi7-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/04906b35de1c97930715a3bf1c4ea200-kix.v5ufyvu2kvi7-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/04906b35de1c97930715a3bf1c4ea200-kix.v5ufyvu2kvi7-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/04906b35de1c97930715a3bf1c4ea200-kix.v5ufyvu2kvi7-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/04906b35de1c97930715a3bf1c4ea200-kix.v5ufyvu2kvi7-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/04906b35de1c97930715a3bf1c4ea200-kix.ey8ik6qi7hg7-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/04906b35de1c97930715a3bf1c4ea200-kix.ey8ik6qi7hg7-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024